Preconditions:
The input array `arr` is not null.
The input array `arr` is not empty.
The input integer `difference` is not null.

Postconditions:
The method returns an integer value representing the length of the longest subsequence in `arr` which is an arithmetic sequence with a difference of `difference`.
The method does not modify the input array `arr`.
If there is no subsequence in `arr` that satisfies the given conditions, the method returns 0.